
<div class="banner d-none d-md-block home_info-banner" style="background-image: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.4),rgba(0,0,0,0.4)), ">
  <div class="container home">
    <h1>Un film à rattraper ?</h1>
    <%= form_with url: movies_path, method: :get, class: "d-flex" do %>
      <%= text_field_tag :query,
        params[:query],
        class: "form-control",
        placeholder: "La soupe aux choux..."
      %>
      <%= button_tag(type: "submit", class: "btn") do %>
        <i class="fa-solid fa-magnifying-glass"></i>
      <% end %>
    <% end %>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="video-background">
  <div class="video-foreground">
    <iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/watch?v=665o5OwV_KU?controls=0&showinfo=0&rel=0&autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=665o5OwV_KU" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"></iframe>
  </div>
</div>

<div id="vidtop-content">
  <div class="vid-info">
	  <p>Un classique à rattraper? Une recommandation que tu ne souhaites pas oublier?    Ne loupe plus rien en nous rejoignant!    Sois averti des (re)sorties et rencontre les cinephiles les plus chauds!</p>
  </div>
</div>
